ucide lucide-search\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><path d=\"m21 21-4.3-4.3\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-foreground hover:scale-110 transition-all border border-border shadow-sm\" aria-label=\"테마 변경\"></button><button class=\"w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-foreground min-[701px]:hidden\" aria-label=\"메뉴\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white text-slate-900 font-sans selection:bg-primary selection:text-white\"><section class=\"relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-slate-950\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-primary/20 blur-[150px] rounded-full animate-pulse\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[150px] rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)] opacity-20\"></div></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 py-20 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-8 animate-bounce\"><span class=\"flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-widest\">비개발자도 OK! AI 시대의 새로운 필수 역량</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8\">코딩을 배우지 마세요.<br/><span class=\"text-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-indigo-400 to-teal-400\">AI를 &#x27;지시하는 방법&#x27;</span>을 배우세요.</h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed\">코드 한 줄 몰라도 웹/앱/프로그램을 만드는 시대.<br/>중요한 건 코딩 실력이 아니라 AI에게 명확히 전달하는 <span class=\"text-white font-bold underline decoration-primary decoration-4 underline-offset-4\">&#x27;지시 능력&#x27;</span>입니다.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16\"><div class=\"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-2xl text-left hover:bg-white/10 transition-all group\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users text-primary w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1\">비개발자도 가능</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs\">누구나 바로 시작</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-2xl text-left hover:bg-white/10 transition-all group\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target text-primary w-5 h-5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1\">실전 결과 중심</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs\">이론 대신 결과물</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-2xl text-left hover:bg-white/10 transition-all group\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap text-primary w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1\">최신 AI 기법</h4><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs\">검증된 실전 노하우</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\"><button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto bg-primary hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-black text-xl transition-all shadow-xl shadow-primary/30 hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-3\">지금 바로 신청하기 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-xl transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3\">프로세스 상세보기</button></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 transition-colors\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16\"><div class=\"flex-1 space-y-8\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight\">이 강의에서 <span class=\"text-primary\">얻는 것</span></h2><ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">AI가 정확히 이해하는 지시 방법</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">디자인 오류를 줄이는 명시적 기술</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">코드 일관성을 유지하는 운영 방식</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">컨텍스트 관리 및 리셋 전략</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">무료 API + LLM 활용법</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold\">실전 프로젝트로 결과물 완성</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[32px] p-10 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-inner\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket text-primary\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg> 만들 수 있는 결과물 예시</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 group hover:border-primary transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><div><h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-0.5\">웹 서비스 / SaaS</h5><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">AI 기반의 비즈니스 서비스</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 group hover:border-primary transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div><h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-0.5\">자동화 프로그램</h5><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">반복 업무 자동화 도구</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 group hover:border-primary transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-download\"><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><polyline points=\"7 10 12 15 17 10\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"15\" y2=\"3\"></line></svg></div><div><h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-0.5\">확장 프로그램</h5><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">브라우저 전용 플러그인</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 group hover:border-primary transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg></div><div><h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-0.5\">모바일 앱</h5><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">하이브리드 방식 앱 제작</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-colors\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6\">이런 <span class=\"text-red-500 italic\">경험</span> 있으신가요?</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg\">AI를 써봐도 원하는 결과가 나오지 않아 답답했던 분들을 위해 준비했습니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-6\">😫</div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3\">코드 오류 반복</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">AI에게 지시했는데 실행되지 않는 이상한 코드만 계속 출력될 때</p></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-6\">😢</div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3\">디자인 레이아웃 깨짐</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">요구사항을 반영해도 전체적인 디자인 밸런스가 무너지고 정렬이 맞지 않을 때</p></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-6\">🤔</div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3\">일관성 없는 결과</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">같은 요청임에도 AI가 매번 다른 답변을 내놓아 관리가 불가능할 때</p></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-6\">😱</div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3\">프로젝트 복잡도 증가</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">파일이 꼬이고 코드가 뒤섞여 어느 순간부터 관리가 전혀 안 될 때</p></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-6\">😵</div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3\">대화 흐름 끊김</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">컨텍스트가 길어지면 AI가 이전 내용을 잊고 엉뚱한 대답을 할 때</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-20 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary flex items-center justify-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb w-8 h-8\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg> 문제는 코딩 실력이 아니라 <span class=\"underline decoration-indigo-300 underline-offset-4\">&quot;AI에게 제대로 지시하지 못한 것&quot;</span>입니다.</h3></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 transition-colors overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6\">새로운 패러다임, <span class=\"text-primary\">바이브 코딩</span></h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg\">개발의 패러다임이 완전히 바뀌고 있습니다.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-center gap-12 lg:gap-20 relative\"><div class=\"flex-1 w-full max-w-md bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-10 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 px-6 py-2 rounded-full w-fit mx-auto text-sm font-black opacity-50 uppercase tracking-widest mb-10\">기존 방식 (코딩 중심)</div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 mt-auto mb-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-6 h-6 text-slate-300\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">문법 학습</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers w-6 h-6 text-slate-300\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">구조 이해</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code-xml w-6 h-6 text-slate-300\"><path d=\"m18 16 4-4-4-4\"></path><path d=\"m6 8-4 4 4 4\"></path><path d=\"m14.5 4-5 16\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">알고리즘</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket w-6 h-6 text-slate-300\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">최종 프로젝트</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-black text-2xl shadow-xl shadow-primary/40 z-10 shrink-0 self-center\">VS</div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full max-w-md bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 rounded-3xl p-10 border-4 border-primary relative flex flex-col\"><div class=\"absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-yellow-400 text-slate-900 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg font-black text-xs shadow-lg animate-bounce\">추천</div><div class=\"bg-primary px-6 py-2 rounded-full w-fit mx-auto text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-widest mb-10\">바이브 코딩 (AI 활용 중심)</div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 mt-auto mb-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-primary text-white border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-6 h-6 text-white\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">목표 정의</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-primary text-white border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square w-6 h-6 text-white\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">명시적 지시 (프롬프트)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-primary text-white border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6 text-white\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">시스템 연계</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 w-full transition-all bg-primary text-white border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-6 h-6 text-white\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">결과물 완성</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-20 text-center\"><p class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">앞으로 개발은 <span class=\"text-red-500\">&quot;잘 짜는 사람&quot;</span>이 아니라<br class=\"md:hidden\"/> <span class=\"text-primary\">&quot;잘 시키는 사람&quot;</span>의 영역입니다.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-colors\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6\">4단계 프로세스</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg\">기초부터 실전 배포까지, 단 4단계의 핵심 프로세스로 마스터하세요.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-8 shadow-sm relative group overflow-hidden text-left flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-purple-500\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500\">01<!-- --> STEP</span></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-6\">AI와 대화하는 법</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-purple-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>AI가 이해하는 명령어 구조</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-purple-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>명확하게 지시하는 법</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-purple-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>실패하는 프롬프트 vs 성공하는 프롬프트</li></ul><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">실습 프로젝트 (2건)</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">프롬프트 엔지니어링 실습 (Basic Chatbot)</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">페르소나 기반 시나리오 설계</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-8 shadow-sm relative group overflow-hidden text-left flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-blue-500\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500\">02<!-- --> STEP</span></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-6\">시스템 이해</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-blue-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>서버 / 클라이언트 개념</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-blue-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>왜 결과가 달라지는지 이해</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-blue-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>컨텍스트와 기억 구조 활용</li></ul><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">실습 프로젝트 (2건)</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">시스템 아키텍처 다이어그램 설계</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">데이터 흐름 시각화 도구 제작</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-8 shadow-sm relative group overflow-hidden text-left flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-teal-500\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">03<!-- --> STEP</span></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-6\">실전 제작</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-teal-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>실제 웹 서비스 만들기</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-teal-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>API 연결 및 기능 확장</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-teal-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>코드 일관성 유지 전략</li></ul><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">실습 프로젝트 (2건)</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">뉴스 큐레이션 웹 서비스 제작</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">개인형 포트폴리오 랜딩페이지</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-8 shadow-sm relative group overflow-hidden text-left flex flex-col h-full hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-orange-500\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500\">04<!-- --> STEP</span></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-6\">배포 &amp; 확장</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>로컬 → 실제 서비스 배포</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>확장 프로그램 / 앱 제작</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>실제 사용 가능한 결과물 완성</li></ul><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">실습 프로젝트 (2건)</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-orange-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">실전 도메인 연결 및 Vercel 배포</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 group/item\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-orange-500 opacity-40 group-hover/item:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover/item:text-primary transition-colors\">크롬 확장 프로그램 (생산성 도구)</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 transition-colors\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-20\">수강 후, <span class=\"text-primary\">이렇게 달라집니다!</span></h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-border rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"p-12 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg> BEFORE</h4><ul class=\"space-y-6\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-slate-200 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-400\">AI에게 계속 다시 설명해야 함</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-slate-200 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-400\">요청할 때마다 결과가 천차만별</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-slate-200 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-400\">디자인 레이아웃이 계속 깨짐</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-slate-200 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-400\">프로젝트가 금방 스파게티 코드가 됨</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-slate-200 text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-400\">완성까지 시간이 오래 걸리고 지침</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"p-12 bg-primary/10 dark:bg-primary/20 relative\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> AFTER</h4><ul class=\"space-y-6 relative z-10\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">한 번에 원하는 결과 도출</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">일관성 있는 코드와 디자인 유지</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">구조적으로 깔끔한 프로젝트 관리</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">AI를 개발자처럼 자유롭게 핸들링</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 group\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125 bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">압도적으로 빠른 속도로 배포 완료</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-colors\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-16\">이런 분들께 <span class=\"text-primary\">강력 추천</span>합니다!</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 break-keep line-clamp-2\">개발을 배우다 포기한 사람</p></div><di